  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV84">
<l>taiyaṉal lārkaḷ kuḻāṅkaṭ kuḻiya kuḻuviṉuḷḷu</l>
<l>maiyanal lārkaḷ kuḻiya viḻaviṉu maṅkaṅkellāṅ</l>
<l>kaiyappoṉ ṉāḻiveṇ caṅkoṭuṅ kāṇpā ṉavāvuvaṉāṉ</l>
<l>maiyavaṇ ṇāmaṇi yēmutta mēyeṉṟaṉ māṇikkamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the crowd that gathers in throngs of good women,</l>
<l>o lord, and in festivals crowded with good people, everywhere,</l>
<l>golden discus in hand with white conch I long to see [you],</l>
<l>you of cloud colour, o sapphire, o pearl, o my ruby.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
